vocabInfos.mediumDef:
A man living at the time of Divided Monarchy, only mentioned at 1Ch.26.2;
son of: Meshelemiah (H4920);
brother of: Zechariah (H2148A), Jediael (H3043J), Zebadiah (H2069J), Elam (H5867H), Jehohanan (H3076I) and Eliehoenai (H0454A)
§ Jathniel = "God hires me"
a Korhite Levite and the 4th of the family of Meshelemiah
vocabInfos._es_Definition: hijo de Meselemías; portero; tribu de Leví
vocabInfos._zh_tw_Definition:
耶提聶 这个陽性專有名詞在原文的意思是 "神雇用我"
可拉的利未人米施利米雅家的四子 (代上26:2)
vocabInfos._zh_Definition:
耶提聂 这个阳性专有名词在原文的意思是 "神雇用我"
可拉的利未人米施利米雅家的四子 (代上26:2)
